OL,3,CFamily of Katie Simpson to take legal
OL,4,Caction against PSNI
OL,6,FThe family of Katie Simpson are suing
OL,7,Fthe Chief Constable over police
OL,8,Ffailings in the initial investigation
OL,9,Finto her death.
OL,11,FThe 21-year-old died in hospital six
OL,12,Fdays after an incident at a property
OL,13,Fnear Londonderry in August 2020.
OL,14,FPolice initially treated her death as
OL,15,Fsuicide.
OL,17,FJonathan Creswell, the partner of Ms
OL,18,FSimpson's sister, was later charged
OL,19,Fwith her murder.
