OL,3,CFamily of Katie Simpson to take legal
OL,4,Caction against PSNI
OL,6,FOn day one of the trial in April 2024,
OL,7,Fit was alleged that Jonathan Creswell
OL,8,Fstrangled the talented Co Armagh
OL,9,Fshowjumper out of jealousy and tried
OL,10,Fto cover it up by making it look like
OL,11,Fshe had attempted to take her own life.
OL,13,FOn day two of the trial, 36-year-old
OL,14,FCreswell was found dead at his home.
OL,16,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher has
OL,17,Fadmitted there were failings in the
OL,18,Finitial investigation and a number of
OL,19,Fofficers are facing disciplinary
OL,20,Faction for misconduct.
