OL,3,CFamily of Katie Simpson to take legal
OL,4,Caction against PSNI
OL,6,FKatie Simpson's family are now taking
OL,7,Flegal action against the PSNI.
OL,9,FTheir solicitor, Kevin Winters, told
OL,10,FUTV: "There is a lot of anger. That
OL,11,Fanger was palpable whenever, in
OL,12,Ffairness to Jon Boucher (PSNI Chief
OL,13,FConstable), he went to the family and
OL,14,Fdelivered a very personal message of
OL,15,Fapology.
OL,17,F"Against that backdrop, they asked me
OL,18,Fabout the various legal remedies that
OL,19,Fare available and we discussed taking
OL,20,Flegal action against the Chief
OL,21,FConstable.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
