OL,3,CFamily of Katie Simpson to take legal
OL,4,Caction against PSNI
OL,6,F"A number of close family relatives
OL,7,Fhave suffered serious PTSD and they
OL,8,Fwill collectively take legal action
OL,9,Fagainst the police".
OL,11,FA Police Ombudsman's report into the
OL,12,Fhandling of the case is set to be made
OL,13,Fpublic in November.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
