OL,6,FUTV has previously revealed some of
OL,7,Fthe Ombudsman's findings in the 1400
OL,8,Fpage document - including how red
OL,9,Fflags were ignored, complaints were
OL,10,Fmade about 18 officers and
OL,11,Fopportunities were missed to gather
OL,12,Fvital evidence with some officers
OL,13,Ftaking Creswell at face value.
OL,15,F"The Ombudsman's report will as I
OL,16,Funderstand be critical of the police.
OL,17,FWhere it lays blame is a matter for
OL,18,Fthe Ombudsman.
OL,20,F"The report will offer some closure
OL,21,Fbut it is not complete closure.
