OL,6,F"This action is about vindication and
OL,7,Fvalidation of their complaints, that
OL,8,Fis why we are taking this legal
OL,9,Faction", Mr Winters added.
OL,11,FIn a statement the PSNI said: "As
OL,12,Fproceedings are ongoing, it would not
OL,13,Fbe appropriate to comment further at
OL,14,Fthis time".
